=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_TwoZero_ex1 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright gritty sound, with complex oscillator character around 53 Hz, featuring punchy attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with highpass character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: gritty
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: highpass
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 52.5164
  harmonic_decay_rate: -0.0182
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0357
  pitch_clarity: 5.1724
  inharmonicity: 0.0510
  type: complex
[filter]
